## Superseded from stale-doc-count-audit

```yaml
name: stale-doc-count-audit
description: Fixing stale numeric counts in documentation (figures, tables, sub-tests,
  source files). Use when a code registry or pipeline changes size but docs still
  reference old counts.
category: documentation
date: 2026-03-13
version: 1.0.0
user-invocable: false
```

Five-step workflow: verify actual count from code (not from docs), fix primary file
with replace_all, search ALL markdown files project-wide, run exploration agent for
cascading staleness, use separate commits for separate fixes.

Critical step: project-wide grep after fixing primary file catches occurrences in
`docs/analysis-prompt.md`, `references/notes.md`, `docs/arxiv-submission.md`.

Verified on: ProjectScylla PR #1477 (27→34 figures across 3 files + 1 subtest count).

