## Superseded from stale-agent-count-fix

```yaml
name: stale-agent-count-fix
description: Fix stale agent count references in documentation after agents are deleted
  or converted to skills.
category: documentation
date: 2026-03-06
version: 1.0.0
user-invocable: false
```

Eight-step workflow: verify actual count (ls .claude/agents/*.md | wc -l), find all
stale count references (grep), update CLAUDE.md in two places (Quick Links + Agent
Hierarchy sections), annotate tracking docs with strikethrough, verify no stale refs,
run pre-commit, run agent validation, commit.

Key parameters: Files to check (CLAUDE.md, agents/hierarchy.md, agents/README.md, docs/dev/*.md);
use Edit tool not sed/awk; strikethrough annotation not deletion; validation command
`python3 tests/agents/validate_configs.py .claude/agents/`.

Failed: `just pre-commit-all` (not in PATH) → use `pre-commit run --all-files`;
mojo-format fails due to GLIBC (pre-existing, not doc-change-caused).

Verified on: ProjectOdyssey PR #3320 (issue #3145), 44→42 agents.

