## Superseded from docs-status-fix

```yaml
name: docs-status-fix
description: "Skill: docs-status-fix"
category: documentation
date: 2026-03-19
version: "1.0.0"
user-invocable: false
```

Four-step workflow: read issue (gh issue view), read relevant CLAUDE.md section,
apply single Edit replacing old status line(s), commit with `fix(docs):` conventional
format. Pre-commit hooks run automatically for markdown validation.

Notes: worktree CLAUDE.md and root CLAUDE.md are separate — check both. Always read
file before editing (Edit tool rejects changes on unread files).

Verified on: ProjectScylla Issue #753, PR #810.

